Triad Election;;81;;96;;NC;;In the wake of his first successful stint at the helm of a Chinese crime syndicate, Lok (Simon Yam) proposes an unheard-of second term. But when government corruption stifles legitimate business interests of Jimmy Lee (Louis Koo) in Hong Kong, the reformed triad operative rises to oppose Lok and regresses into a life of crime. As the conflict erupts into all-out gangland war, the business-minded Lee becomes increasingly brutal in his desperation to secure a comfortable future for his family.;;Drama,Crime,Mystery & thriller;;Johnnie To;;2007;;Louis Koo,Simon Yam,Nick Cheung,Siu-Fai Cheung,Suet Lam;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/election_2